 and wants to know what information is needed. Let me think about what's needed for a GPA calculator.\n\nA GPA calculator typically needs:\n- Course names\n- Credits/credit hours for each course\n- Grades (letter grades or percentage scores)\n- The grading scale being used\n\nLet me ask the user what format they'd like and what information they can provide.","signature":"","modelProvider":"anthropic","notionModelName":"avocado-froyo-medium"},{"type":"text","content":"当然可以帮你做一个 GPA 计算工具！为了更好地帮你搭建，我需要了解以下几点：\n\n### 需要你提供的信息\n\n1. **GPA 计算方式**：你用的是哪种绩点制？\n   - 4.0 制（常见于北美）\n   - 5.0 制\n   - 百分制转绩点（国内常见，比如北大算法、标准算法等）\n\n2. **课程信息**：每门课需要包含哪些内容？\n   - 课程名称\n   - 学分\n   - 成绩（字母等级如 A/B/C，还是百分制分数？）\n\n3. **你的课程数据**：\n   - 你已经有课程列表了吗？可以直接告诉我\n   - 还是先建一个空的数据库，之后自己填写？\n\n你告诉我这些，我就可以帮你创建一个带自动计算 GPA 的 Notion 数据库 🎓"}],"traceId":"d96c82b1-bc12-4dea-9f0f-4a74ea671694","startedAt":1772709124051,"finishedAt":1772709135780,"inputTokens":32898,"outputTokens":421,"cachedTokensRead":32412,"cachedTokensCreated":1226,"maxContextTokens":200000,"maxInputTokens":160000,"model":"avocado-froyo-medium"},"parent_id":"a4eb51fd-3414-4968-a03d-ce49a638fb9d","parent_table":"thread","created_by_id":"314d872b-594c-8100-bff4-0002d949d4a4","created_by_table":"notion_user","created_time":1772709129160,"data":{"inference_id":"d96c82b1-bc12-4dea-9f0f-4a74ea671694","completed":true,"completed_time":1772709135822}},"role":"editor"}}}}}
